{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything except the electric wires, the machines, and the human beings that were around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything else was salt, the ceiling, the walls, the floor, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So these were like rock salt that had to be mined out, which was done by slave laborers during World War II.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It is an old mine, but it was enlarged and widened and-- for World War II-- during World War II.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The streets were called Adolf-Hitler-Strasse, Hermann-Goring-Strasse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all the top Nazis received the honor of having one of these streets named after them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My job was to-- well, my job was to make parts for precision instruments.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, these are-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were precision instruments for the V1 and V2 rockets, and these were the rockets used by the Germans during World War II.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that the Parliament building in London was hit, and quite a bit of damage was done to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And other European capitals were affected by it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Allies feared these most.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Hitler took us out of the camp-- out of Auschwitz to do these jobs important to Germany, in other words, to help with the German war effort.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was 15 years old at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was assigned to work on a machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A German man, a civilian man, trained me how to do this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, I was selected to do this job in-- in Hamburg, where industrialists were sent into the camp to hand-pick those who would work in the underground factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The way we were picked was by holding our hands up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I thought that we-- we were being punished at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I didn't know why, but we got used to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There need not be a reason to be punished.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
